  `bitstring_default`/`bitstring_err`, the `Some`/`None`/
  `True`/`False`/`nat_lit` constructors, `logical_and`/`or`, and
  every `rust_primitives::*` / `core::*` / `hax_lib::*` opaque
  function the extraction surface needs.
*)


